WEBVTT

00:02.333 --> 00:07.708
SO WHAT´S THE BIG DEAL ABOUT
THIS QUINCEAN...HOO-HA?

00:07.708 --> 00:09.380
IT´S CALLED
A QUINCEAÑERA.

00:09.380 --> 00:11.512
IT´S LIKE
A LATINA DEBUTANTE BALL.

00:11.512 --> 00:13.784
IT´S WHEN A YOUNG GIRL BECOMES
A WOMAN, LIKE A SWEET 16,

00:13.784 --> 00:15.686
BUT YOU DO IT
WHEN YOU´RE 15.

00:15.686 --> 00:17.648
I DID IT WHEN I WAS 14.

00:19.720 --> 00:21.722
YOU HAD
A QUINCEAÑERA?

00:21.722 --> 00:24.425
OKAY.

00:28.028 --> 00:29.430
HEY, KIDS.

00:29.430 --> 00:30.301
HEY, DADDY.

00:30.301 --> 00:31.502
HEY, MR. LOPEZ.

00:31.502 --> 00:33.033
OH, WHAT
YOU GOT THERE?

00:33.033 --> 00:35.035
OH, ANGIE´S
DRY CLEANING.

00:35.035 --> 00:37.037
OH, THAT´S SO NICE.

00:37.037 --> 00:40.441
[ IMITATING WHIP CRACKING ]

00:40.441 --> 00:42.343
YEAH, YOU WOULD KNOW
THAT WHIP SOUND.

00:42.343 --> 00:44.575
THAT´S HOW THEY GET YOU
IN THE BARN AT NIGHT.

00:46.547 --> 00:49.220
GOD, I WISH I COULD
FIGURE OUT THIS STUPID DRESS.

00:49.220 --> 00:51.582
I WOULDN´T SPEND
TOO MUCH TIME ON IT.

00:51.582 --> 00:53.454
THAT DRESS
IS JUST GONNA END UP

00:53.454 --> 00:56.087
IN THE BACKSEAT
OF THAT GUY´S CAR ANYWAY.

00:56.087 --> 00:56.587
MOM!

00:56.587 --> 00:57.758
WHAT?!

00:57.758 --> 00:59.730
WHY´S CARMEN
MAKING A DRESS ANYWAY?

00:59.730 --> 01:01.632
WELL, SHE WANTS TO
SPARE YOU SOME MONEY.

01:01.632 --> 01:04.265
YOU´RE SPENDING
SO MUCH ON THE QUINCEAÑERA.

01:04.265 --> 01:07.198
WHAT? THERE´S NOT
GONNA BE A QUINCEAÑERA.

01:07.198 --> 01:09.640
OH, NOW, THAT´S NOT
WHAT ANGIE SAYS.

01:09.640 --> 01:11.172
WELL THAT´S WHAT I SAY.

01:11.172 --> 01:13.444
SHE KNOWS WE CAN´T AFFORD
A BIG PARTY RIGHT NOW.

01:13.444 --> 01:15.176
I THOUGHT
SHE CALLED IT OFF.

01:15.176 --> 01:18.279
WELL, DON´T YOU WORRY YOUR
PRETTY, BIG HEAD ABOUT IT.

01:21.182 --> 01:23.714
YOU KNOW,
YOUR HUSBAND´S WORKING.

01:23.714 --> 01:25.556
SHE CAN PAY FOR IT.

01:27.087 --> 01:32.693
OH, NO, SHE´S HOME, AND YOU,
WITH NO DINNER ON THE TABLE.

01:32.693 --> 01:35.196
PUT AN APPLE IN YOUR MOUTH,
JUMP IN THE OVEN,

01:35.196 --> 01:37.468
AND I´LL SERVE BAT.

01:38.129 --> 01:39.500
[ SMOOCHES ]

01:39.500 --> 01:41.432
HEY, I THOUGHT YOU
CALLED OFF THE QUINCEAÑERA.

01:41.432 --> 01:42.503
WHY WOULD
YOU THINK THAT?

01:42.503 --> 01:44.175
OH, I DON´T KNOW,
ANGIE.

01:44.175 --> 01:46.437
BECAUSE I´M OUT OF WORK
AND WE CAN´T AFFORD IT?

01:46.437 --> 01:49.240
HONEY, WE CAN´T GET
THE DEPOSIT BACK ON THE HALL

01:49.240 --> 01:51.242
AND THE INVITATIONS
HAVE GONE OUT

01:51.242 --> 01:53.244
AND WE HAVE
PEOPLE FLYING IN.

01:53.244 --> 01:56.217
BUT THIS IS CRAZY.
YOUR SALARY IS BARELY
COVERING OUR BILLS.

01:56.217 --> 01:59.220
IF WE CANCEL,
IT´LL DEVASTATE HER.

01:59.220 --> 02:02.323
AGAIN?

02:02.323 --> 02:05.656
LIKE THAT TIME HER LIP GLOSS
ROLLED UNDER THE REFRIGERATOR?

02:07.858 --> 02:10.301
LOOK, WE´RE NOT WASTING
OUR MONEY ON SOME PARTY.

02:10.301 --> 02:13.504
YOU´RE THINKING ABOUT THIS
THE WRONG WAY.

02:13.504 --> 02:16.207
WE ARE CREATING MEMORIES
FOR OUR DAUGHTER.

02:16.207 --> 02:17.738
HOW IS THAT A WASTE?

02:17.738 --> 02:19.910
"CREATING MEMORIES
FOR OUR DAUGHTER."

02:19.910 --> 02:22.713
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

02:22.713 --> 02:26.477
WELL...THE PARTY
CAN´T BE CANCELED.

02:26.477 --> 02:28.148
YES, IT CAN,
AND IT WILL BE.

02:28.148 --> 02:30.150
THEN YOU GO GIVE HER THE NEWS,
´CAUSE I´M NOT GOING TO.

02:30.150 --> 02:31.322
I´LL DO IT.

02:31.322 --> 02:33.153
YOU GO BREAK
YOUR DAUGHTER´S HEART.

02:33.153 --> 02:35.826
I´LL BREAK HER HEART.
I´LL DO IT RIGHT NOW.

02:37.358 --> 02:39.260
I´M LIKE THAT, ANGIE.
WATCH OUT.

02:39.260 --> 02:41.692
HEARTBREAKER.

02:43.234 --> 02:46.166
AFTER THE FATHER-DAUGHTER DANCE,
I´M OFFICIALLY A WOMAN.

02:46.166 --> 02:49.770
OH, SO HOW SOON CAN YOU START
USING YOUR WOMANHOOD, HUH?

02:51.672 --> 02:53.574
YOU GO ANYWHERE
NEAR HER WOMANHOOD

02:53.574 --> 02:55.606
AND YOU´LL BE
LOOKING FOR YOUR MANHOOD

02:55.606 --> 02:57.348
AT THE BOTTOM
OF A PUNCHBOWL.

02:57.348 --> 02:58.449
I´M SORRY, SIR.

02:58.449 --> 02:59.610
BYE, JASON.

03:00.781 --> 03:02.853
HEY, CARMEN,
WE NEED TO TALK.

03:02.853 --> 03:04.585
SO, WHAT DO
YOU THINK, DADDY?

03:04.585 --> 03:06.587
IT´S GONNA BE WHITE,
COVERED IN FAUX PEARLS,

03:06.587 --> 03:07.888
AND I´M GONNA WEAR A TIARA.

03:07.888 --> 03:09.320
TIARA?

03:09.320 --> 03:10.861
CARMEN, D-DON´T
YOU THINK QUINCEAÑERAS

03:10.861 --> 03:12.723
ARE KIND OF A LITTLE
OLD-FASHIONED?

03:12.723 --> 03:16.327
HELLS NO!
IT´S RETRO, BRO!

03:16.327 --> 03:18.198
YEAH, ALL MY FRIENDS
THINK IT´S COOL.

03:18.198 --> 03:21.372
IT´S GONNA BE THE BEST
PARTY OF THE YEAR.

03:21.372 --> 03:24.475
YEAH, BUT...CARMEN,
WE´RE AMERICANS.

03:24.475 --> 03:26.477
YOU KNOW,
WE´RE ASSIMILATED.

03:26.477 --> 03:28.479
HOW´S THAT GONNA LOOK
TO THE NEIGHBORS?

03:28.479 --> 03:30.481
A LATINO FAMILY
HAVING A QUINCEAÑERA.

03:30.481 --> 03:32.443
I MEAN,
IT´S SO OBVIOUS.

03:33.844 --> 03:36.487
THAT´S ONE OF THE REASONS
I DON´T GET A LEAF BLOWER.

03:36.487 --> 03:39.420
A MEXICAN AND A LEAF BLOWER,
WHO WANTS TO SEE THAT?

03:41.752 --> 03:42.993
OH!

03:42.993 --> 03:44.355
WHAT´S THAT FOR?

03:44.355 --> 03:45.856
I KNOW MONEY´S
TIGHT RIGHT NOW,

03:45.856 --> 03:48.359
BUT I JUST WANT TO THANK YOU
FOR GIVING ME WHAT I KNOW

03:48.359 --> 03:50.961
IS GONNA BE ONE OF THE
GREATEST DAYS OF MY LIFE.

03:50.961 --> 03:53.003
YEAH.

03:53.003 --> 03:54.665
MEMORIES -- PRICELESS.

03:54.665 --> 03:57.508
WELL, NOT ACTUALLY PRICELESS,
BUT, WELL, THERE YOU ARE.

04:00.441 --> 04:02.473
HOW´D SHE TAKE IT?

04:02.473 --> 04:06.417
I THINK WE SHOULD
TELL HER TOGETHER.

04:06.417 --> 04:08.779
I KNEW YOU
COULDN´T DO IT.

04:08.779 --> 04:10.451
HONEY, LISTEN.

04:10.451 --> 04:12.853
AFTER ALL THE BAD STUFF THAT
THIS FAMILY´S BEEN THROUGH,

04:12.853 --> 04:14.885
IT´S ABOUT TIME
WE CELEBRATE SOMETHING.

04:14.885 --> 04:17.488
BUT WHAT ARE
WE CELEBRATING, ANGIE?

04:17.488 --> 04:19.460
ALL SHE DID WAS TURN 15.

04:20.791 --> 04:22.793
I´LL TELL YOU WHAT.
LET´S SAVE THE MONEY.

04:22.793 --> 04:25.265
WHEN SHE MOVES OUT,
WE´LL HAVE A PARTY THEN.

04:25.265 --> 04:27.438
THEN WE CAN
ALL CELEBRATE.

04:29.870 --> 04:32.573
LISTEN, I KNOW IT´S
HARD FOR YOU TO UNDERSTAND

04:32.573 --> 04:34.975
BECAUSE YOU´VE NEVER
BEEN A TEENAGE GIRL.

04:36.847 --> 04:40.611
MY QUINCEAÑERA -- IT WAS
A DAY I WILL NEVER FORGET.

04:40.611 --> 04:43.283
I-I DRESSED UP
LIKE CINDERELLA,

04:43.283 --> 04:47.588
AND MY FRIENDS AND I
PUT ON A BIG MUSICAL SHOW,

04:47.588 --> 04:50.561
AND FOR ONE DAY
I WAS A PRINCESS.

04:50.561 --> 04:52.863
WELL, YOU PROBABLY
WON´T UNDERSTAND THIS

04:52.863 --> 04:56.667
BECAUSE YOU´VE NEVER BEEN
A MAN IN DEBT, BUT WHO CARES?!

04:59.970 --> 05:03.003
GEORGE, WE ARE
HAVING THIS PARTY.

05:03.003 --> 05:06.777
MNH-MNH. NO, I DON´T WANT
TO SPEND THE MONEY.

05:06.777 --> 05:09.980
WELL, IT´S NOT
YOUR DECISION.

05:09.980 --> 05:13.484
EXCUSE ME?

05:13.484 --> 05:15.446
I´M WORKING.
YOU´RE NOT.

05:15.446 --> 05:17.588
IT´S MY MONEY.
IT´S MY DECISION.

05:17.588 --> 05:18.689
THAT´S IT.

05:20.421 --> 05:21.992
THAT´S NOT IT!

05:21.992 --> 05:23.824
I´M DONE
TALKING ABOUT THIS!

05:23.824 --> 05:25.456
WELL I´M NOT DONE
TALKING ABOUT IT!

05:25.456 --> 05:27.858
YEAH, YOU´RE LUCKY I GOTTA
PUT SOME FABRIC SOFTENER

05:27.858 --> 05:30.631
IN THE RINSE CYCLE,
OR THIS COULD GET UGLY!

05:32.733 --> 05:36.737
IT ALREADY HAS,
PRINCESS.

05:36.737 --> 05:39.540
[ INTRO TO WAR´S "LOW RIDER"
PLAYS ]

05:50.020 --> 05:54.024
♫ ALL MY FRIENDS
KNOW THE LOW RIDER ♫

05:56.026 --> 06:01.392
♫ THE LOW RIDER
IS A LITTLE HIGHER ♫

06:26.857 --> 06:28.519
OH, MOM?
HMM?

06:28.519 --> 06:30.461
I WANT TO MENTION JASON
IN MY SPEECH FOR THE PARTY,

06:30.461 --> 06:32.392
BUT I CAN´T DECIDE
WHAT TO CALL HIM.

06:32.392 --> 06:34.825
IF I CALL HIM MY BOYFRIEND,
IT MIGHT FREAK HIM OUT.

06:34.825 --> 06:36.597
BUT IF I CALL HIM
MY FRIEND,

06:36.597 --> 06:38.729
HE MIGHT THINK
I DON´T CARE ABOUT HIM.

06:38.729 --> 06:41.101
SHOULD I JUST CALL HIM
MY SPECIAL FRIEND?

06:45.105 --> 06:47.007
JUST KEEP IT LOW-KEY.

06:47.007 --> 06:50.481
WHEN YOU TALK ABOUT YOUR
FRIENDS, MENTION JASON, TOO.

06:50.481 --> 06:53.143
AND THEN, RIGHT AFTER
YOU SAY HIS NAME,

06:53.143 --> 06:56.887
LOOK AT HIM, AND GIVE HIM
A LITTLE SMILE.

06:58.789 --> 07:01.091
OH, THAT´S GOOD!

07:01.091 --> 07:02.593
OKAY!

07:02.593 --> 07:05.456
"I´D LIKE TO THANK ALL
MY FRIENDS FOR COMING --

07:05.456 --> 07:09.730
UM, MICHELLE, OLIVIA,
TAYLOR, KATIE, AND JASON."

07:13.063 --> 07:14.905
SHOULD I TAKE
A BIGGER PAUSE?

07:14.905 --> 07:18.509
I SHOULD, SHOULDN´T I?
I´LL TAKE A BIGGER PAUSE.

07:18.509 --> 07:20.170
MOM, SHOULD I TAKE
A BIGGER PIECE OF CAKE?

07:20.170 --> 07:21.612
I SHOULD, SHOULDN´T I?

07:21.612 --> 07:23.844
I´LL TAKE A BIGGER
PIECE OF CAKE.

07:23.844 --> 07:25.516
SHUT UP, IDIOT.

07:25.516 --> 07:26.647
COME ON, SPECIAL CAKE.

07:26.647 --> 07:28.679
YOU´RE MY SPECIAL,
SPECIAL...

07:28.679 --> 07:30.080
SHUT UP!

07:37.057 --> 07:40.931
LISTEN, HONEY,
I´VE BEEN THINKING.

07:40.931 --> 07:43.634
I GOT A LITTLE
CARRIED AWAY YESTERDAY.

07:43.634 --> 07:45.666
I KNOW YOU´RE
IN A WEIRD PLACE

07:45.666 --> 07:47.738
´CAUSE YOU´RE
NOT WORKING RIGHT NOW.

07:47.738 --> 07:49.540
I SHOULD´VE BEEN
A LITTLE MORE SENSITIVE.

07:49.540 --> 07:53.674
LOOK, CARMEN CAN HAVE
HER QUINCEAÑERA, OKAY?

07:53.674 --> 07:56.106
I DON´T WANT
TO DENY MY DAUGHTER.

07:56.106 --> 07:58.549
BUT JUST DON´T
GO OVERBOARD, OKAY?

07:58.549 --> 07:59.750
[ MARACAS SHAKING ]

08:00.951 --> 08:03.684
Man: 5...6...7...8...

08:03.684 --> 08:06.717
A 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8.

08:06.717 --> 08:09.720
1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8.

08:09.720 --> 08:12.623
1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8.

08:12.623 --> 08:14.494
1, 2, 3, 4...

08:17.868 --> 08:21.201
I COULD´VE SWORN I PLANTED THE
GAY DANCERS IN THE FRONT YARD.

08:21.201 --> 08:22.673
Shh!

08:27.538 --> 08:31.612
THEY´RE REHEARSING THE INTRO
FOR CARMEN´S CALYPSO NUMBER.

08:31.612 --> 08:35.185
DO YOU MIND STARTING FROM THE
BEGINNING SO WE CAN BOTH SEE?

08:35.185 --> 08:36.847
SURE.

08:41.151 --> 08:42.893
[ CALYPSO MUSIC PLAYS ]

08:42.893 --> 08:46.226
5...6...7...8...

09:00.811 --> 09:02.973
[ MUSIC STOPS ]

09:02.973 --> 09:05.676
THAT WAS GREAT!
WASN´T THAT GREAT?

09:05.676 --> 09:07.918
WE´RE DOING KIND OF
AN UNDER THE SEA THING.

09:07.918 --> 09:09.980
JUST PICTURE THEM
DRESSED AS SEA HORSES.

09:09.980 --> 09:12.052
AND AT THE END OF THE NUMBER,

09:12.052 --> 09:15.225
CARMEN COMES OUT
OF A GIANT OYSTER SHELL.

09:18.729 --> 09:19.960
THAT´S GREAT.

09:19.960 --> 09:23.263
NOW...PICTURE US
AS HOMELESS PEOPLE...

09:23.263 --> 09:26.997
PUSHING THE GIANT OYSTER
SHELL, COLLECTING CANS.

09:29.569 --> 09:30.841
GEORGE!

09:30.841 --> 09:33.874
I KNOW YOU´RE MAD AT ME,
BUT GET OVER IT!

09:33.874 --> 09:35.876
THIS IS NOT
ABOUT US ANYMORE.

09:35.876 --> 09:37.207
THIS IS ABOUT CARMEN,

09:37.207 --> 09:40.280
AND I AM NOT GONNA
LET YOU RUIN THIS FOR HER.

09:40.280 --> 09:42.012
GEORGE!

09:42.012 --> 09:44.985
THEY´RE CLOSING DOWN
THE FACTORY FOR GOOD!

09:44.985 --> 09:46.917
JACK´S GOING ON THE LAM.

09:46.917 --> 09:47.988
HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?

09:47.988 --> 09:49.589
I WENT
DOWN TO THIRSTY´S,

09:49.589 --> 09:51.822
AND ERNIE TOLD ME
THAT FRANK TOLD HIM

09:51.822 --> 09:55.926
THAT GINA SAW JACK AT THE
AIRPORT BUYING A TICKET.

09:59.299 --> 10:02.032
THAT´S IT!
IT´S OVER.

10:02.032 --> 10:04.775
WE CAN´T HAVE THE QUINCEAÑERA.
MY JOB´S GONE!

10:04.775 --> 10:07.908
DO YOU TWO HEAR YOURSELVES?
YOU´RE BEING RIDICULOUS.

10:07.908 --> 10:10.010
LOOK, ANGIE,
WE´RE BEING INVESTIGATED

10:10.010 --> 10:11.712
FOR A CRASH
THAT KILLED TWO PEOPLE.

10:11.712 --> 10:13.714
THE OWNER OF THE COMPANY
IS FLEEING THE COUNTRY.

10:13.714 --> 10:15.916
W-WHAT OTHER
EXPLANATION IS THERE?!

10:15.916 --> 10:17.788
THAT HE´S
GOING ON VACATION

10:17.788 --> 10:21.191
AND A BUNCH OF DRUNKS AT A BAR
JUMPED TO A CONCLUSION?

10:21.191 --> 10:25.055
I HEARD
HE HAD A STRAW HAT ON.

10:27.928 --> 10:29.229
THAT´S IT!

10:29.229 --> 10:31.702
WHY?
WHY IS THAT IT?

10:31.702 --> 10:33.133
BECAUSE IF YOU´RE
GOING ON VACATION,

10:33.133 --> 10:34.805
YOU BUY THE HAT THERE.

10:34.805 --> 10:37.367
IF YOU´RE FLEEING THE COUNTRY,
YOU TAKE THE HAT WITH YOU!

10:37.367 --> 10:38.939
THINK, ANGIE!

10:38.939 --> 10:42.342
GEORGE, CALM DOWN.

10:42.342 --> 10:44.875
EVERYONE IS JUST
GETTING SCARED

10:44.875 --> 10:47.047
BECAUSE THIS INVESTIGATION
IS TAKING A WHILE.

10:47.047 --> 10:49.950
YOU´RE WORRYING ABOUT
THINGS THAT YOU DON´T
EVEN KNOW ARE TRUE.

10:49.950 --> 10:52.823
YOU´RE BOTH
ACTING CRAZY.

10:52.823 --> 10:54.184
NOW, IF YOU´LL EXCUSE ME,

10:54.184 --> 10:57.087
THERE ARE FOUR TIRED
SEA HORSES IN THE BACKYARD

10:57.087 --> 10:58.328
WHO NEED ORANGE JUICE.

11:00.230 --> 11:04.094
WE´RE CALLING THEM
SEA HORSES NOW?

11:32.863 --> 11:36.266
[ CONCH BLOWS ]

11:36.266 --> 11:39.369
[ CALYPSO MUSIC PLAYS ]

11:41.271 --> 11:44.134
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

11:52.943 --> 11:54.745
[ WHISTLING ]

12:04.124 --> 12:07.758
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

12:07.758 --> 12:09.429
[ WHISTLING ]

12:16.907 --> 12:21.912
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
OUR BEAUTIFUL BIRTHDAY GIRL,

12:21.912 --> 12:25.375
CARMEN CONSUELO LOPEZ!

12:25.375 --> 12:27.818
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

12:29.479 --> 12:31.051
CONSUELO?

12:31.051 --> 12:33.183
WELL, IT´S SOMEBODY
WHO WAS IMPORTANT TO ANGIE

12:33.183 --> 12:35.155
FROM THE PAST
OR SOMETHING.

12:35.155 --> 12:36.486
OH...

12:39.029 --> 12:41.792
ON BEHALF OF MY HUSBAND
AND MYSELF

12:41.792 --> 12:45.465
AND MY GUARDIAN ANGEL
WHO IS ALWAYS WITH ME,

12:45.465 --> 12:48.238
MY GRANDMOTHER
CONSUELO...

12:48.238 --> 12:51.201
OH, YEAH, THAT´S IT.

12:51.201 --> 12:54.274
...I´D LIKE TO THANK
EVERYONE FOR JOINING US

12:54.274 --> 12:57.347
TO CELEBRATE OUR
LITTLE GIRL´S COMING OF AGE!

12:57.347 --> 12:58.879
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

13:03.854 --> 13:09.119
I WOULD ALSO LIKE TO THANK
MY HUSBAND, GEORGE...

13:09.119 --> 13:12.092
[ APPLAUSE ]

13:14.094 --> 13:18.098
...FOR ALL THE LOVE AND
EMOTIONAL SUPPORT HE PROVIDED

13:18.098 --> 13:20.831
DURING THE CRAZY
PARTY PLANNING.

13:20.831 --> 13:24.935
NOW, PLEASE, EVERYONE,
ENJOY YOURSELVES!

13:24.935 --> 13:26.306
[ CALYPSO MUSIC PLAYS ]

13:31.942 --> 13:34.114
"LOVE AND EMOTIONAL
SUPPORT"?

13:34.114 --> 13:35.185
GEORGE...

13:37.247 --> 13:39.890
WHY DON´T YOU JUST
TELL EVERYBODY I DON´T
HAVE ANY MONEY?

13:39.890 --> 13:42.522
I DIDN´T SAY
ANYTHING ABOUT MONEY.

13:42.522 --> 13:44.855
LOOK, YOU DON´T
HAVE TO SAY IT, ANGIE.

13:44.855 --> 13:46.356
THEY KNOW!

13:46.356 --> 13:48.398
YOU´RE BEING RIDICULOUS.

13:48.398 --> 13:52.362
THAT WAS SO COLD, SAYING
MY SON DOESN´T HAVE ANY MONEY.

13:52.362 --> 13:53.833
I DIDN´T SAY THAT!

13:53.833 --> 13:55.936
EVERYONE KNOWS
THAT A MAN WHO HAS A JOB

13:55.936 --> 13:58.408
DOESN´T NEED TO GIVE
HIS WIFE EMOTIONAL SUPPORT.

13:58.408 --> 14:02.242
DO YOU THINK YOUR ONLY VALUE
TO THIS FAMILY IS A PAYCHECK?

14:02.242 --> 14:03.974
THAT´S MY JOB
IN THIS FAMILY.

14:03.974 --> 14:06.146
WHEN I WAS A KID,
MY MOM ALWAYS COMPLAINED

14:06.146 --> 14:09.149
ABOUT HOW THERE WASN´T A MAN
AROUND TO HELP WITH THE BILLS.

14:09.149 --> 14:11.521
LOOK, A MAN ISN´T A MAN
UNLESS HE´S A PROVIDER.

14:11.521 --> 14:13.423
I´M A HUNTER!
I´M A PROVIDER!

14:13.423 --> 14:15.025
HUNTER?

14:15.025 --> 14:17.888
YOU CAN´T EVEN GIVE
THE DOG EYEDROPS!

14:17.888 --> 14:19.859
IF HE LOOKED AWAY,
I COULD.

14:23.593 --> 14:26.136
I THINK
WHAT YOU CAN´T HANDLE

14:26.136 --> 14:29.099
IS THE FACT THAT
I´M THE PROVIDER NOW.

14:29.099 --> 14:30.640
UH, NO...
WHAT I CAN´T HANDLE

14:30.640 --> 14:32.372
IS YOU MAKING
ALL THE MONEY DECISIONS.

14:32.372 --> 14:35.605
THINK I LIKED DEFERRING TO YOU
WHEN YOU WERE THE BREADWINNER?

14:35.605 --> 14:38.278
WELL...NO ONE
SHOULD BE DEFERRING.

14:40.580 --> 14:44.214
AGREED.
NO MORE "MY MONEY."

14:44.214 --> 14:47.387
COME ON, IT´S "OUR MONEY."
WE´RE A TEAM.

14:47.387 --> 14:48.658
YES, SWEETHEART.

14:48.658 --> 14:50.620
[ MUSIC STOPS ]

14:50.620 --> 14:53.393
CAN I HAVE EVERYONE´S
ATTENTION, PLEASE?

14:53.393 --> 14:57.527
UM, FIRST I WOULD
LIKE TO THANK MY PARENTS.

14:57.527 --> 15:01.101
MOM, DAD, I KNOW THAT I DON´T
TELL YOU GUYS THIS ENOUGH,

15:01.101 --> 15:04.674
BUT I REALLY APPRECIATE ALL THE
SACRIFICES THAT YOU MAKE FOR ME,

15:04.674 --> 15:06.306
AND I LOVE YOU BOTH.

15:06.306 --> 15:08.338
[ SMOOCHES ]

15:10.310 --> 15:14.584
YESTERDAY I WAS A MERE CHILD
THINKING CHILDISH THOUGHTS.

15:14.584 --> 15:16.246
I´LL KILL HIM.
Shh!

15:18.518 --> 15:20.090
BUT TODAY I AM A WOMAN

15:20.090 --> 15:22.252
STANDING ON THE PRECIPICE
OF LIFE´S MYSTERIES.

15:22.252 --> 15:24.124
[ GROANS ]

15:24.124 --> 15:27.297
KEEP ´EM COMING, AND DON´T STOP
UNTIL I´M DEAF IN BOTH EARS.

15:27.297 --> 15:30.100
AND SO THIS IS
THE BEGINNING OF MY JOURNEY.

15:30.100 --> 15:33.603
TO MY FRIENDS, THANK YOU
SO MUCH FOR BEING THERE.

15:33.603 --> 15:39.109
THANK YOU, MICHELLE, OLIVIA,
TAYLOR, KATIE, AND JASON.

15:46.246 --> 15:49.519
YOU ARE THE RADIANT SUN THAT
WAKES ME UP IN THE MORNING.

15:49.519 --> 15:54.985
THE GLIMMERING MOON THAT
ILLUMINATES MY DREAMS.

15:54.985 --> 15:59.029
I LOVE YOU
MORE THAN LIFE ITSELF.

16:00.730 --> 16:03.033
MY JASON!

16:03.994 --> 16:05.395
[ APPLAUSE ]

16:08.098 --> 16:11.201
THANK YOU, EVERYONE.
ENJOY THE REST OF THE PARTY.

16:13.343 --> 16:16.676
I THINK WE´RE
SUPPOSED TO DANCE NOW.

16:16.676 --> 16:20.010
UH...I´M ALLERGIC
TO SHELLFISH.

16:20.010 --> 16:22.012
I GOTTA GO.

16:22.012 --> 16:24.614
A LITTLE ADVICE.

16:24.614 --> 16:29.989
WHEN IT COMES TO MEN,
THAT IS THE ENEMY OF THOSE.

16:31.661 --> 16:36.666
WILL EVERYONE PLEASE
RAISE THEIR GLASS IN A TOAST

16:36.666 --> 16:39.029
FOR OUR BIRTHDAY GIRL.

16:39.029 --> 16:41.031
YOU KNOW, IT SEEMS LIKE
JUST YESTERDAY...

16:41.031 --> 16:43.002
GEORGE, GEORGE,
GEORGE, GEORGE!

16:43.002 --> 16:45.004
DUDE, I JUST
GOT A CALL FROM JACK.

16:45.004 --> 16:47.677
HE TOLD ME TO TELL YOU
THE INVESTIGATION´S OVER!

16:47.677 --> 16:49.279
WE´RE NOT RESPONSIBLE
FOR THE CRASH!

16:49.279 --> 16:51.311
IT WAS PILOT ERROR!
WE´RE GOING BACK TO WORK!

16:51.311 --> 16:53.043
I´M GOING BACK TO WORK?!
YEAH!

16:53.043 --> 16:56.146
GREAT NEWS --
I DIDN´T KILL ANYONE!

16:57.587 --> 17:00.350
AND I´M NOT HERE
FOR EMOTIONAL SUPPORT!

17:00.350 --> 17:03.493
I´M A PROVIDER AGAIN!
THE HUNTER´S BACK!

17:05.055 --> 17:08.058
A TOAST...

17:08.058 --> 17:12.062
...TO PILOT ERROR.

17:13.763 --> 17:17.337
OH, YEAH, A-AND CARMEN!

17:17.337 --> 17:20.340
EVERYBODY, ENJOY
THE QUINCEAÑERA!

17:23.373 --> 17:25.475
ISN´T THAT GREAT, BABY?
I GOT MY JOB BACK!

17:25.475 --> 17:28.448
YES! BUT WHAT WAS THAT
ABOUT "THE HUNTER´S BACK"?

17:28.448 --> 17:31.721
OH, WE HAVE MY SALARY.
THIS PARTY´S NOT GONNA KILL US.

17:31.721 --> 17:34.824
CARMEN ENDED UP MAKING
A FOOL OUT OF HERSELF.

17:37.127 --> 17:39.389
EVERYTHING IS BACK
TO NORMAL AGAIN.

17:39.389 --> 17:42.132
WE´RE STILL GONNA SHARE THE
FINANCIAL DECISIONS, RIGHT?

17:42.132 --> 17:43.833
ANGIE, LET´S NOT WORRY
ABOUT THAT RIGHT NOW.

17:43.833 --> 17:45.695
LOOK, IT´S OUR
DAUGHTER´S QUINCEAÑERA.

17:45.695 --> 17:48.368
ENJOY!
ENJOY!

17:48.368 --> 17:51.141
IT´S STILL GONNA BE
OUR MONEY, RIGHT?

17:51.141 --> 17:52.842
ANGIE, WHAT IS IT
WITH YOU AND MONEY?

17:52.842 --> 17:55.345
YOU SHOULD BE DANCING.

17:55.345 --> 17:57.207
SO WE
ARE STILL A TEAM?

17:57.207 --> 17:59.649
YES, WE´RE A TEAM,
AND I´M THE QUARTERBACK.

17:59.649 --> 18:00.580
[ SMOOCHES ]

18:00.580 --> 18:02.312
THIS IS SO NOT OVER.

18:02.312 --> 18:04.284
DON´T WORRY, YOU CAN STILL
PROVIDE EMOTIONAL SUPPORT.

18:04.284 --> 18:05.815
LOOK, A CONGA LINE!

18:26.276 --> 18:28.278
WHY THE SAD FACE?

18:28.278 --> 18:30.140
DAD, I CALLED JASON,
LIKE, 15 TIMES

18:30.140 --> 18:31.441
AND HE HASN´T
CALLED ME BACK.

18:31.441 --> 18:33.783
CARMEN, LET ME TEACH YOU
A LITTLE SOMETHING

18:33.783 --> 18:35.445
ABOUT BOYS YOUR AGE.

18:35.445 --> 18:37.887
NEVER TELL THEM
WHAT THEY MEAN TO YOU.

18:37.887 --> 18:40.190
NEVER, EVER SAY,
"I LOVE YOU!"

18:41.491 --> 18:45.625
AND NEVER, EVER DO THIS WHILE
COMING OUT OF A GIANT CLAM.

18:47.527 --> 18:50.600
LOOK, JUST GIVE JASON
SOME SPACE AND SOME TIME.

18:50.600 --> 18:51.701
HE´LL GET OVER IT.

18:51.701 --> 18:53.233
HOW LONG SHOULD I WAIT?

18:53.233 --> 18:55.365
WELL, WHY DON´T YOU WAIT
TILL HE CALLS YOU BACK?

18:55.365 --> 18:57.567
IN THE MEANTIME, YOU CAN
HAVE SOME MORE BOYFRIENDS,

18:57.567 --> 18:59.339
MAYBE A HUSBAND,
A FEW KIDS.

18:59.339 --> 19:01.271
CARMEN, IT´S OVER.
MOVE ON!

19:04.574 --> 19:06.876
GEORGE, I THINK THE MOTOR
ON THE WASHING MACHINE IS SHOT.

19:06.876 --> 19:08.278
DO YOU THINK
WE SHOULD GET A NEW ONE?

19:08.278 --> 19:09.819
NO, I´LL TRY
TO FIX IT AGAIN.

19:09.819 --> 19:12.322
I DON´T WANT TO SPEND
THAT KIND OF MONEY RIGHT NOW.

19:12.322 --> 19:15.154
[ SIGHS ] OKAY.
IT´S YOUR DECISION.

19:15.154 --> 19:17.687
MY DECISION
WAS TO BUY A NEW ONE.

19:17.687 --> 19:19.259
I HAD IT PUT IN
THIS MORNING.

19:19.259 --> 19:22.262
WITHOUT TALKING TO ME?

19:22.262 --> 19:23.493
YEP.

19:23.493 --> 19:26.196
I WROTE A CHECK
OFF OUR JOINT ACCOUNT.

19:26.196 --> 19:28.298
OH [CHUCKLES] OKAY,
I GET IT.

19:28.298 --> 19:31.541
YOU´RE STILL UPSET ABOUT
ME BEING THE QUARTERBACK.

19:31.541 --> 19:33.573
YOU´RE RIGHT, BABY.
WE SHOULD BE A TEAM.

19:33.573 --> 19:34.704
[ SMOOCHES ]

19:34.704 --> 19:36.476
YES, WE SHOULD.

19:36.476 --> 19:38.648
WHAT KIND OF
WASHER DID YOU WANT --

19:38.648 --> 19:40.380
TOP-LOADER
OR FRONT-LOADER?

19:40.380 --> 19:41.451
TOP-LOADER!

19:41.451 --> 19:44.384
OH...SO CLOSE.

19:50.620 --> 19:52.792
[ CALYPSO MUSIC PLAYS ]

20:03.503 --> 20:06.676
HEY, ALL RIGHT!
WHAT A CROWD, WHAT A CROWD.

20:06.676 --> 20:08.508
LOOK AT THIS ONE, HUH?

20:08.508 --> 20:11.381
IT LOOKS LIKE NEPTUNE
HAD A YARD SALE.

20:11.381 --> 20:12.782
[ LAUGHS ]

20:12.782 --> 20:14.614
IT´S LIKE MAKING
MY ENTRANCE FROM THE URINAL

20:14.614 --> 20:15.715
AT THE SEAFOOD BROILER.

20:15.715 --> 20:17.787
[ LAUGHS ]

20:17.787 --> 20:19.449
HEY, ERNIE, CALL YOUR MOM.

20:19.449 --> 20:21.921
TELL HER I FOUND
HALF OF HER BIKINI TOP.

20:21.921 --> 20:23.523
[ LAUGHS ]

20:25.895 --> 20:27.797
GEORGE, I´VE BEEN WAITING
IN THE CAR.

20:27.797 --> 20:29.459
ARE YOU COMING OR NOT?

20:29.459 --> 20:31.761
NO! I PAID THESE
SEA HORSES TILL MIDNIGHT.

20:31.761 --> 20:36.366
OKAY, BOYS, ONE MORE TIME, AND
THIS TIME WITH HEART, HONEY!

20:36.366 --> 20:37.867
[ CALYPSO MUSIC PLAYS ]

20:41.741 --> 20:52.251
TRY TO KEEP UP.
